underlying_goal: To debug why Claude Code might not be starting by analyzing recent git changes.
primary_success: Correctly identified that machine-specific runtime state files (`installed_plugins.json`) were committed to git, explaining that the hardcoded absolute paths were the likely root cause of the startup issue.
brief_summary: The user asked for an analysis of a git diff to find the cause of a startup issue. Claude correctly identified hardcoded absolute paths in committed runtime plugin files as the root cause. It explained the problem clearly and proposed the correct fix of git-ignoring the files, which the user accepted.
